120 (h) In addition to any other penalty that may be
121 provided for under this chapter, the board may levy a fine not
122 to exceed fifty dollars ($50) per day for each day the
123 certificate holder fails to file its annual statement, and the
124 board may levy a fine not to exceed fifty dollars ($50) per
